{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":820,"text":"So, I'm an artist."},{"time":2468,"text":"I live in New York, and I've been working in advertising"},{"time":4922,"text":"for -- ever since I left school,"},{"time":7567,"text":"so about seven, eight years now,"},{"time":9188,"text":"and it was draining."},{"time":10744,"text":"I worked a lot of late nights. I worked a lot of weekends,"},{"time":13457,"text":"and I found myself never having time for all the projects"},{"time":16627,"text":"that I wanted to work on on my own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18929,"text":"And one day I was at work and I saw a talk"},{"time":20891,"text":"by Stefan Sagmeister on TED,"},{"time":23122,"text":"and it was called \"The power of time off,\""},{"time":24777,"text":"and he spoke about how every seven years,"},{"time":27413,"text":"he takes a year off from work so he could"},{"time":29520,"text":"do his own creative projects, and I was instantly inspired,"},{"time":33185,"text":"and I just said, \"I have to do that. I have to take a year off."},{"time":36574,"text":"I need to take time to travel and spend time with my family"},{"time":41053,"text":"and start my own creative ideas.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":43339,"text":"So the first of those projects ended up being"},{"time":46978,"text":"something I called \"One Second Every Day.\""},{"time":50544,"text":"Basically I'm recording one second of every day of my life"},{"time":52878,"text":"for the rest of my life,"},{"time":55613,"text":"chronologically compiling these one-second"},{"time":58550,"text":"tiny slices of my life into one single continuous video"},{"time":62852,"text":"until, you know, I can't record them anymore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68529,"text":"The purpose of this project is, one:"},{"time":70886,"text":"I hate not remembering things that I've done in the past."},{"time":75610,"text":"There's all these things that I've done with my life"},{"time":78320,"text":"that I have no recollection of"},{"time":80234,"text":"unless someone brings it up, and sometimes I think,"},{"time":81950,"text":"\"Oh yeah, that's something that I did.\""},{"time":85521,"text":"And something that I realized early on in the project"},{"time":87162,"text":"was that if I wasn't doing anything interesting,"},{"time":89886,"text":"I would probably forget to record the video."},{"time":92365,"text":"So the day -- the first time that I forgot, it really hurt me,"},{"time":95838,"text":"because it's something that I really wanted to --"},{"time":98313,"text":"from the moment that I turned 30, I wanted"},{"time":100509,"text":"to keep this project going until forever,"},{"time":103859,"text":"and having missed that one second, I realized,"},{"time":106305,"text":"it just kind of created this thing in my head"},{"time":110058,"text":"where I never forgot ever again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115598,"text":"So if I live to see 80 years of age,"},{"time":118597,"text":"I'm going to have a five-hour video"},{"time":121230,"text":"that encapsulates 50 years of my life."},{"time":123979,"text":"When I turn 40, I'll have a one-hour video"},{"time":126371,"text":"that includes just my 30s."},{"time":131608,"text":"This has really"},{"time":133136,"text":"invigorated me day-to-day, when I wake up,"},{"time":136411,"text":"to try and do something interesting with my day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146757,"text":"Now, one of the things that I have issues with is that,"},{"time":150265,"text":"as the days and weeks and months go by,"},{"time":154463,"text":"time just seems to start blurring"},{"time":156280,"text":"and blending into each other"},{"time":158202,"text":"and, you know, I hated that,"},{"time":161933,"text":"and visualization is the way to trigger memory."},{"time":174992,"text":"You know, this project for me is a way for me"},{"time":177881,"text":"to bridge that gap and remember everything that I've done."},{"time":181175,"text":"Even just this one second allows me to remember"},{"time":183742,"text":"everything else I did that one day."},{"time":186019,"text":"It's difficult, sometimes, to pick that one second."},{"time":188681,"text":"On a good day, I'll have maybe three or four seconds"},{"time":191865,"text":"that I really want to choose,"},{"time":193578,"text":"but I'll just have to narrow it down to one,"},{"time":195727,"text":"but even narrowing it down to that one allows me"},{"time":197691,"text":"to remember the other three anyway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200171,"text":"It's also kind of a protest, a personal protest,"},{"time":203712,"text":"against the culture we have now where people"},{"time":206107,"text":"just are at concerts with their cell phones out"},{"time":208549,"text":"recording the whole concert, and they're disturbing you."},{"time":210698,"text":"They're not even enjoying the show."},{"time":211933,"text":"They're watching the concert through their cell phone."},{"time":215038,"text":"I hate that. I admittedly used to be that guy a little bit,"},{"time":219006,"text":"back in the day, and I've decided that the best way"},{"time":221824,"text":"for me to still capture and keep a visual memory of my life"},{"time":227405,"text":"and not be that person, is to just record that one second"},{"time":230491,"text":"that will allow me to trigger that memory of,"},{"time":232760,"text":"\"Yeah, that concert was amazing. I really loved that concert.\""},{"time":236135,"text":"And it just takes a quick, quick second."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241553,"text":"I was on a three-month road trip this summer."},{"time":244432,"text":"It was something that I've been dreaming about doing my whole life,"},{"time":247286,"text":"just driving around the U.S. and Canada"},{"time":249779,"text":"and just figuring out where to go the next day,"},{"time":253018,"text":"and it was kind of outstanding."},{"time":255623,"text":"I actually ran out, I spent too much money on my road trip"},{"time":259335,"text":"for the savings that I had to take my year off,"},{"time":262325,"text":"so I had to, I went to Seattle and I spent some time"},{"time":265219,"text":"with friends working on a really neat project."},{"time":276111,"text":"One of the reasons that I took my year off was to spend more time with my family,"},{"time":279871,"text":"and this really tragic thing happened where"},{"time":283281,"text":"my sister-in-law,"},{"time":284886,"text":"her intestine suddenly strangled one day,"},{"time":288322,"text":"and we took her to the emergency room,"},{"time":291100,"text":"and she was, she was in really bad shape."},{"time":294392,"text":"We almost lost her a couple of times,"},{"time":296467,"text":"and I was there with my brother every day."},{"time":303908,"text":"It helped me realize something else during this project,"},{"time":306684,"text":"is that recording that one second on a really bad day"},{"time":313199,"text":"is extremely difficult."},{"time":314432,"text":"It's not -- we tend to take our cameras out when we're doing awesome things."},{"time":319629,"text":"Or we're, \"Oh, yeah, this party, let me take a picture.\""},{"time":322053,"text":"But we rarely do that when we're having a bad day,"},{"time":325055,"text":"and something horrible is happening."},{"time":326936,"text":"And I found that it's actually been very, very important"},{"time":330356,"text":"to record even just that one second of a really bad moment."},{"time":333900,"text":"It really helps you appreciate the good times."},{"time":337601,"text":"It's not always a good day, so when you have a bad one,"},{"time":341888,"text":"I think it's important to remember it,"},{"time":343786,"text":"just as much as it is important to remember the [good] days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357480,"text":"Now one of the things that I do is I don't use any filters,"},{"time":360346,"text":"I don't use anything to -- I try to capture the moment"},{"time":364125,"text":"as much as possible as the way that I saw it with my own eyes."},{"time":369752,"text":"I started a rule of first person perspective."},{"time":372487,"text":"Early on, I think I had a couple of videos where"},{"time":374560,"text":"you would see me in it, but I realized that wasn't the way to go."},{"time":378773,"text":"The way to really remember what I saw"},{"time":380620,"text":"was to record it as I actually saw it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392537,"text":"Now a couple of things that I have in my head about this project are,"},{"time":396799,"text":"wouldn't it be interesting if thousands of people were doing this?"},{"time":402774,"text":"I turned 31 last week, which is there."},{"time":409029,"text":"I think it would be interesting to see"},{"time":410757,"text":"what everyone did with a project like this."},{"time":412605,"text":"I think everyone would have a different interpretation of it."},{"time":414597,"text":"I think everyone would benefit from just having that one second to remember every day."},{"time":419335,"text":"Personally, I'm tired of forgetting,"},{"time":422186,"text":"and this is a really easy thing to do."},{"time":424757,"text":"I mean, we all have HD-capable cameras in our pockets right now --"},{"time":427626,"text":"most people in this room, I bet --"},{"time":429456,"text":"and it's something that's --"},{"time":431046,"text":"I never want to forget another day that I've ever lived,"},{"time":433304,"text":"and this is my way of doing that,"},{"time":435585,"text":"and it'd be really interesting also to see,"},{"time":438370,"text":"if you could just type in on a website,"},{"time":440340,"text":"\"June 18, 2018,\""},{"time":443546,"text":"and you would just see a stream of people's lives"},{"time":445897,"text":"on that particular day from all over the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447591,"text":"And I don't know, I think this project has a lot of possibilities,"},{"time":450813,"text":"and I encourage you all to record just a small snippet of your life every day,"},{"time":454460,"text":"so you can never forget that that day, you lived."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456307,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":458011,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}